(6, 1, '2012-08-11 17:19:07', '2012-08-11 17:19:07', 'At The Refinery, we home-make and bake nearly everything we sell. Eight types of bread, all ice-cream, cakes, pastry and biscuits, we dry our own tomatoes, make our own pesto, tapenade, salad dressings and sauces, we make yoghurt, Turkish yoghurt, burgers, French fries, pasta, gnocchi, you name it, it’s made by us. That way we know that we are not feeding you additives, colourings, taste enhancers, nothing that’s harmful to the health. With soups and sauces, we don’t “cheat”, we use home-made vegetable, chicken or fish stock, not corn starch and granules.', 'Homemade', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'homemade', '', '', '2012-08-30 01:22:56', '2012-08-30 01:22:56', '', 0, 'http://www.therefinerysaigon.com/wordpress/?page_id=6', 0, 'page', '', 0),
